---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="硬件加密与数据主权 — U-Key · SIMKey · Signal · 本地 Ollama | ChainlessChain"
  description="ChainlessChain 安全架构：U-Key/SIMKey 硬件芯片（私钥永不导出）、AES-256 + SQLCipher 全量加密、Signal 协议端到端、本地 Ollama 推理。4 项发明专利，等保三级认证。"
  canonical="https://www.chainlesschain.com/security"
>
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-ink text-cream">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-grid-ink opacity-50 pointer-events-none"></div>
    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-[600px] h-[600px] rounded-full bg-ember/10 blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>
    <div class="container-wide relative pt-20 pb-24 md:pt-32 md:pb-32">
      <div class="max-w-4xl">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs bg-line-dark text-muted-dark mb-6 animate-fade-in">
          <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-ember rounded-full"></span> 安全架构
        </div>
        <h1 class="animate-fade-in-delay font-display text-6xl md:text-display-lg leading-[1.02]">
          密钥从不<br/><span class="italic text-ember">离开你的设备</span>。
        </h1>
        <p class="animate-fade-in-delay-2 mt-8 text-xl text-muted-dark leading-relaxed max-w-3xl">
          从硬件芯片到本地模型，我们在每一层都选择了"数据不出境"的实现。
          不是"承诺不上云"，是"物理上无法上云"。
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Architecture diagram -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="container-wide">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mb-10">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl mb-4">数据流向，看得见的边界</h2>
        <p class="text-muted">加粗的实线是数据会流经的路径，被划掉的虚线是被切断的路径。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-line p-6 md:p-10 bg-cream/40">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 900 380" class="w-full h-auto" role="img" aria-label="ChainlessChain 安全架构图">
          <style>
            .node { fill: #FAF9F5; stroke: #1E1E1C; stroke-width: 1.5; }
            .node-dark { fill: #1E1E1C; stroke: #1E1E1C; stroke-width: 1.5; }
            .node-ember { fill: #D97757; stroke: #D97757; }
            .label { font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif; font-size: 16px; fill: #1E1E1C; }
            .label-light { font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif; font-size: 16px; fill: #F4F3ED; }
            .caption { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 10px; fill: #6B6A65; }
            .flow { stroke: #1E1E1C; stroke-width: 2; fill: none; }
            .blocked { stroke: #D97757; stroke-width: 2; fill: none; stroke-dasharray: 4 4; }
          </style>
          <!-- User -->
          <rect x="30" y="160" width="140" height="60" rx="8" class="node" />
          <text x="100" y="185" text-anchor="middle" class="label">用户</text>
          <text x="100" y="205" text-anchor="middle" class="caption">You</text>

          <!-- U-Key / SIMKey -->
          <rect x="220" y="100" width="180" height="80" rx="8" class="node-ember" />
          <text x="310" y="130" text-anchor="middle" class="label-light">U-Key · SIMKey</text>
          <text x="310" y="150" text-anchor="middle" font-family="JetBrains Mono" font-size="10" fill="#1E1E1C">私钥永不导出</text>
          <text x="310" y="165" text-anchor="middle" font-family="JetBrains Mono" font-size="10" fill="#1E1E1C">AES-256 · ECC</text>

          <!-- Encrypted DB -->
          <rect x="220" y="210" width="180" height="80" rx="8" class="node" />
          <text x="310" y="240" text-anchor="middle" class="label">SQLCipher 数据库</text>
          <text x="310" y="260" text-anchor="middle" class="caption">AES-256 加密</text>
          <text x="310" y="275" text-anchor="middle" class="caption">密钥由 U-Key 管理</text>

          <!-- Local Ollama -->
          <rect x="450" y="160" width="200" height="60" rx="8" class="node-dark" />
          <text x="550" y="185" text-anchor="middle" class="label-light">本地 Ollama</text>
          <text x="550" y="205" text-anchor="middle" font-family="JetBrains Mono" font-size="10" fill="#D97757">qwen2 · llama3 · deepseek</text>

          <!-- P2P -->
          <rect x="450" y="60" width="200" height="60" rx="8" class="node" />
          <text x="550" y="85" text-anchor="middle" class="label">P2P · Signal 协议</text>
          <text x="550" y="105" text-anchor="middle" class="caption">端到端加密</text>

          <!-- Cloud (crossed) -->
          <rect x="720" y="160" width="140" height="60" rx="8" fill="none" stroke="#D97757" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-dasharray="4 4" />
          <text x="790" y="185" text-anchor="middle" class="label" fill="#D97757">云端 / 服务器</text>
          <text x="790" y="205" text-anchor="middle" class="caption" fill="#D97757">数据永不上云</text>
          <line x1="730" y1="170" x2="850" y2="210" stroke="#D97757" stroke-width="2" />
          <line x1="850" y1="170" x2="730" y2="210" stroke="#D97757" stroke-width="2" />

          <!-- Flows -->
          <path d="M 170 190 L 220 140" class="flow" marker-end="url(#arrow)" />
          <path d="M 170 190 L 220 250" class="flow" marker-end="url(#arrow)" />
          <path d="M 400 190 L 450 190" class="flow" marker-end="url(#arrow)" />
          <path d="M 400 140 L 450 90" class="flow" marker-end="url(#arrow)" />
          <path d="M 650 190 L 720 190" class="blocked" />
          <defs>
            <marker id="arrow" viewBox="0 0 10 10" refX="10" refY="5" markerWidth="6" markerHeight="6" orient="auto-start-reverse">
              <path d="M 0 0 L 10 5 L 0 10 z" fill="#1E1E1C"/>
            </marker>
          </defs>

          <!-- Legend -->
          <text x="30" y="340" class="caption">━━ 实际数据流</text>
          <text x="180" y="340" class="caption" fill="#D97757">- - - 被切断的路径</text>
        </svg>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Detailed sections -->
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="container-wide space-y-20">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-[auto,1fr] gap-10 md:gap-16">
        <div class="md:w-48 shrink-0">
          <div class="font-mono text-xs text-ember mb-2">01</div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-3xl">U-Key</h3>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed mb-4">USB 安全芯片，Windows 平台通过 Koffi FFI 直连 SIMKey SDK。</p>
          <p class="prose-muted mb-4">密钥在安全芯片内生成与使用，永不离开硬件。签名、加密、数据库密钥管理均需 U 盾物理确认，多次 PIN 错误自动锁定。macOS / Linux 自动降级为软件模拟模式。</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="chip">Koffi FFI</span>
            <span class="chip">PIN 保护</span>
            <span class="chip">BLE / NFC 无线</span>
            <span class="chip">生物识别</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-[auto,1fr] gap-10 md:gap-16">
        <div class="md:w-48 shrink-0">
          <div class="font-mono text-xs text-ember mb-2">02</div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-3xl">SIMKey</h3>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed mb-4">SIM 卡硬件安全，Android OMAPI / iOS eSIM API 接入。</p>
          <p class="prose-muted mb-4">利用 SIM 卡内置安全芯片，覆盖三大运营商 USIM 与 5G 超级 SIM 卡。12 大安全增强：eSIM OTA、NFC 离线签名、TEE 深度集成、量子抗性、卫星通信 SIM、HSM 联合认证。</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="chip">OMAPI</span>
            <span class="chip">eSIM</span>
            <span class="chip">TEE 集成</span>
            <span class="chip">卫星通信</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-[auto,1fr] gap-10 md:gap-16">
        <div class="md:w-48 shrink-0">
          <div class="font-mono text-xs text-ember mb-2">03</div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-3xl">AES-256 · SQLCipher</h3>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed mb-4">本地数据库全量加密，密钥由 U-Key 守护。</p>
          <p class="prose-muted">SQLite + SQLCipher，WAL 模式 + busy_timeout 保证并发，参数化查询防注入。密钥从不以明文落盘，每次解锁都需硬件签名。</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-[auto,1fr] gap-10 md:gap-16">
        <div class="md:w-48 shrink-0">
          <div class="font-mono text-xs text-ember mb-2">04</div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-3xl">Signal 协议</h3>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed mb-4">P2P 消息端到端加密 · Double Ratchet。</p>
          <p class="prose-muted">前向安全 + 后向安全。离线消息队列 + 自动重发。结合 libp2p + WebRTC 实现 NAT 穿透。</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-[auto,1fr] gap-10 md:gap-16">
        <div class="md:w-48 shrink-0">
          <div class="font-mono text-xs text-ember mb-2">05</div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-3xl">本地 Ollama</h3>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed mb-4">敏感数据强制本地模型推理。</p>
          <p class="prose-muted">LLMManager 智能路由：敏感标记 → Ollama；普通任务 → 用户选择的 provider。14+ 云 LLM 可选但绝不默认。所有 prompt / response 在本地留痕。</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-[auto,1fr] gap-10 md:gap-16">
        <div class="md:w-48 shrink-0">
          <div class="font-mono text-xs text-ember mb-2">06</div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-3xl">合规与认证</h3>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed mb-4">等保三级 · 4 项发明专利 · 团体标准参编。</p>
          <p class="prose-muted">参编 <span class="font-mono">T/ZGCMCA 023—2025</span> AI 团体标准。企业版支持完整的审计日志、DLP 策略引擎、SIEM 导出（CEF / LEEF / JSON）、SOC2 证据自动收集。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-24">
    <div class="container-wide max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl mb-6">默克尔树证书 (MTC) — 后量子安全压缩</h2>
      <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed mb-6">
        借鉴 IETF PLANTS WG 协议，把后量子签名（SLH-DSA-128f）切换后单证书 17 KB 暴涨问题压回 ~700 B —— <strong>节省约 97%</strong>。
      </p>
      <ul class="text-lg leading-relaxed list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-6">
        <li>批量签发 + RFC 6962 Merkle 树 + 域分离前缀（防签名重放）</li>
        <li>Split-view 攻击防御（同 namespace + tree_size 不同根 → MTCA_DOUBLE_SIGNED 拒绝）</li>
        <li>多种传输：内存 / 文件系统 drop-zone / 真 libp2p（TCP+Noise+Yamux）+ gossipsub</li>
        <li>verifier 守护进程 <code>cc mtc serve</code> 自动订阅 + 持久化 + 篡改检测</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="prose-muted">
        Phase 1 + 1.5 已完整落地（154 测试全绿）。审计日志双轨签名路径阻塞于合规复核（等保三级 / T/ZGCMCA 023—2025 条款）。详见
        <a href="https://docs.chainlesschain.com/guide/mtc-merkle-tree-certs" class="underline">用户使用指南</a>
        与
        <a href="https://design.chainlesschain.com/mtc-landing-plan" class="underline">设计文档</a>。
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-24 bg-ink text-cream">
    <div class="container-wide text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl mb-6">对安全有更严格要求？</h2>
      <p class="text-muted-dark text-lg mb-8">我们为金融、医疗、政企客户提供门限签名、HSM 集成、PQC 迁移、MTC 多模式 MTCA 部署等深度定制方案。</p>
      <a href="tel:400-1068-687" class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 px-8 py-4 rounded-md bg-ember text-ink font-display text-2xl hover:bg-ember-dark transition-colors">
        <span>☎</span><span class="tracking-tight">400-1068-687</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
